                  rdfs:subClassOf obo:BFO_0000016 ;
                  rdfs:label "magnetic susceptibility"@en ;
                  skos:definition "Magnetic susceptibility is a disposition of a material which describes how responsive the material is to an applied magnetic field. It is a relation between the induced magnetization M and the magnetic field H."@en ;
                  co:symbol "χ"@en .


